<lb ed="I" n="0043b01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0043b0101">熙平二年太歲在丁酉三月<unclear cert="low" reason="damage"/>丙酉朔□日壬戌
<lb ed="I" n="0043b02" type="honorific"/>　比丘劉僧<unclear cert="low" reason="damage"/>真少□道門。志□於外。□□□累
<lb ed="I" n="0043b03" type="honorific"/>　<note n="0043001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">刼＝劫【史】</note><app n="0043001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">劫</lem><rdg wit="【原】">刼</rdg></app>之苦。□□有在□□緣以□□□□□□
<lb ed="I" n="0043b04" type="honorific"/>　臨高照之<unclear cert="low" reason="damage"/>隆□。並四時□□□□□樂逾□
<lb ed="I" n="0043b05" type="honorific"/>天宮。供施精巖。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage"/>使<unclear cert="low" reason="damage"/>外□万路歸□。道俗恭□連
<lb ed="I" n="0043b06" type="honorific"/>車蓋疋興逮。上為皇帝延綿。師僧先<unclear cert="low" reason="damage"/>妣。造石像
<lb ed="I" n="0043b07" type="honorific"/>一<note n="0043002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">駈＝軀【史】</note><app n="0043002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">軀</lem><rdg wit="【原】">駈</rdg></app>。興福以誌。願皇帝隆綿。師僧父母。朗朗與
<lb ed="I" n="0043b08" type="honorific"/>三光並暈。覆則与乾<unclear cert="low" reason="damage"/>晨<unclear cert="low" reason="damage"/>同□。下為四部道俗欽
<lb ed="I" n="0043b09" type="honorific"/>明。核業藏潤。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage"/>宿信<note n="0043003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𢏏＝彌【史】</note><app n="0043003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">彌</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𢏏</rdg></app>樂。敬崇三寶。□智龍天。任
<lb ed="I" n="0043b10" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="low" reason="damage"/>顥皇朝有類氏人女□□□外渡四碍。除充主
<lb ed="I" n="0043b11" type="honorific"/>公<unclear cert="low" reason="damage"/>郡想。競業疇延。室家和望。眾陳天<note n="0043004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">笇＝算【史】</note><app n="0043004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">算</lem><rdg wit="【原】">笇</rdg></app>正始<unclear cert="low" reason="damage"/>智
<lb ed="I" n="0043b12" type="honorific"/>然合邑子等。閻石記<unclear cert="low" reason="damage"/>念。永世留名。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage"/>為<unclear cert="low" reason="damage"/>恐事記願
<lb ed="I" n="0043b13" type="honorific"/>登覽首。未<unclear cert="low" reason="damage"/>來世中。彌勒三會。□等蓋□。願願從
<lb ed="I" n="0043b14" type="honorific"/>心。三有群生。普同成佛。</p>
